@node "RobMission 12"
Well this is were i decided a couple of pics may be in order.You are given
an oil well and simply need a solar plant and refinery to make use of
it.Basically you are attacked from the NE and SE and so need to block these
points and eventually build defenses to protect them.To the NE i recommend a
ws01 and to SE a couple of ws03 try and place your units behind
the buildings to the NE as the ws01 can hurt you.From the very beginning you
can start to deplete the Humans' energy supply by looking for a rapid fire
nest to the north of your confines and attacking it with a rocket
launcher.Really try to position your units inside your base perimeter ready
to fire upon approaching enemy without hurting each other don't put your
heavy weapons in a block or they will trip over each other.Take the enemy
oil well NE of your base but not b4 producing a mobile cv. which you should
deploy north of this well,applying a ws01 on the SE corner only when there
is enough power.when you have the cosmic center produce a spy plane to give
a complete map of the battlefield.If you produce giant antigrav you can
finish off the mission easily
@endnode
@node "RobMission 13"
I have noticed that when you start the Mission it is called Mission 14 and
not 13*DUH*.Before you start this mission make sure that you have the
crimsoncrisis patch from clickbooms portal or you cannot finish it.This
mission appears hard as you start to run out of oil quite quickly.The enemy
can gain access to your base from the north and SE.They have a tendency to
attack your barracks with Sioux so send a laser tank near to it.generally
keep an eye on your base to watch for sneak sioux attacks.Artillery are a bi
your defences,they can destroy ws02 and ws01 easily with one shot if you do
not keep your defences repaired.When you start running out of oil send a
saboteur and oil driller to that well NE.there is also another well SW,but
to utilise this efficiently you will need a mobile cv so you can place
defenses nearby.A mobile cv. is obtained by upgrading the light factory i
beleive.i shall try to provide .gif of my ase etc to aid ppl.when placing
ws01 place them all alone.the reason for this is that if triple tanks come
right next to them and there are two ws01 they may destroy each
other.Eventually the constant attacks wil cease and this is the right time
to produce {"thunderbolt" link "thunderbolt"}.to take out enemy derfences.The oil wellsx2 to the NE
of the map are full so take these first b4 other wells.The enemy silos are
full so take them with technicians and be careful with the thunderbolts
around them they have a nasty habit of destroying stuff.
@endnode
