@node "Infantry"
Infantry are good at close quarter combat in groups of four or more.I tend to
use them as a last line of defence guarding my base.They can be squashed by
medium and heavy units.Under no circumstances let them attack enemy buildings if
it's about to blow as they will be shredded by the shrapnel.
@endnode
